In the mixed halide perovskite, the transition from tetragonal to cubic phase occurs at temperature ~ 330 K19,42 due to the tilted inorganic PbI6 octahedral and disparity of organic CH3N H3+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
